Thank you.

197
00:16:10,970 --> 00:16:12,638
I can't look back.

198
00:16:13,973 --> 00:16:15,599
I didn't look back.

199
00:16:19,979 --> 00:16:22,648
They say it's bad luck
to watch somebody leave.

200
00:16:27,361 --> 00:16:29,571
