Keep going.
Supper's gonna be ready when we get in.

216
00:18:09,254 --> 00:18:11,048
What good is a deed?

217
00:18:13,925 --> 00:18:18,514
My grandfathers and great uncles,
grandmothers and great aunts,

218
00:18:18,597 --> 00:18:20,349
father and mother,

219
00:18:20,432 --> 00:18:25,479
