1049
01:21:33,638 --> 01:21:37,392
Hey. It's okay. It's okay. Jamie.
It's okay. It's okay.

1050
01:21:37,475 --> 01:21:42,606
It's me. It's me. It's okay. It's okay.

1051
01:21:46,818 --> 01:21:48,820
