1059
01:22:43,375 --> 01:22:45,085
You need to take me to town.

1060
01:22:46,503 --> 01:22:48,421
I'm gonna kill Carl.

1061
01:22:51,508 --> 01:22:53,885
Vera, why don't you come
and sit down and we'll talk...

1062
