1150
01:33:26,225 --> 01:33:27,393
We'll be okay.

1151
01:33:28,728 --> 01:33:31,814
He'll be okay once he has his own place.

1152
01:33:31,897 --> 01:33:33,107
We'll be okay?

1153
01:33:33,607 --> 01:33:35,818
