1155
01:33:55,755 --> 01:33:58,925
Yes, I do.

1156
01:33:59,884 --> 01:34:04,013
You know what? You ain't supposed to be up
on that broke leg all the time, Jackson.

1157
01:34:05,306 --> 01:34:07,683
If you don't let it heal,
